OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly mist, patchy fog or low
OL,6,Fcloud will gradually disperse leaving
OL,7,Fbright conditions with high cloud.
OL,8,FBecoming warm inland again, except
OL,9,Fcooler across Kent and also for other
OL,10,Fcoastal areas.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cloudy start to the evening
OL,13,Fwith some coastal showers. The cloud
OL,14,Fwill break inland but linger around
OL,15,Fthe coasts. Ground frost patches
OL,16,Fpossible in rural areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
